\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|1,503\n|1,154\n|-\n|56\n|Trije\u0161nica\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|290\n|496\n|-\n|57\n|Trnjaci\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|639\n|1,074\n|-\n|58\n|Velika Obarska\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|3,549\n|3,902\n|-\n|59\n|Velino Selo\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|451\n|342\n|-\n|60\n|Vr\u0161ani\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|1,249\n|614\n|-\n|61\n|Zagoni\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|1,766\n|619\n|}\n\n===Ethnic composition===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"8\" |Ethnic composition \u2013 Bijeljina city\n|-\n|\n|2013.\n|1991.\n|1981.\n|1971.\n|-\n|Total\n|42,278 (100,0%)\n|36,414 (100,0%)\n|31,124 (100,0%)\n|24,761 (100,0%)\n|-\n|Serbs\n|35,798 (84,67%)\n|10,450 (28,70%)\n|7,866 (25,27%)\n|7,630 (30,81%)\n|-\n|Bosniaks\n|4,469 (10,57%)\n|19,024 (52,24%)\n|15,015 (48,24%)\n|14,929 (60,29%)\n|-\n|Others\n|632 (1,495%)\n|3,122 (8,574%)\n|521 (1,674%)\n|349 (1,409%)\n|-\n|Unaffiliated\n|502 (1,187%)\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|Roma\n|338 (0,799%)\n|\n|976 (3,136%)\n|104 (0,420%)\n|-\n|Croats\n|315 (0,745%)\n|366 (1,005%)\n|409 (1,314%)\n|677 (2,734%)\n|-\n|Yugoslavs\n|127 (0,300%)\n|3,452 (9,480%)\n|6,028 (19,37%)\n|637 (2,573%)\n|-\n|Unknown\n|35 (0,083%)\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|Montenegrins\n|29 (0,069%)\n|\n|60 (0,193%)\n|71 (0,287%)\n|-\n|Macedonians\n|14 (0,033%)\n|\n|64 (0,206%)\n|63 (0,254%)\n|-\n|Slovenes\n|11 (0,026%)\n|\n|17 (0,055%)\n|20 (0,081%)\n|-\n|Albanians\n|8 (0,019%)\n|\n|144 (0,463%)\n|237 (0,957%)\n|-\n|Hungarians\n|\n|\n|24 (0,077%)\n|44 (0,178%)\n|}<br />\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"8\" |Ethnic composition \u2013 Bijeljina municipality\n|-\n|\n|2013.\n|1991.\n|1981.\n|1971.\n|-\n|Total\n|107,715 (100,0%)\n|96,988 (100,0%)\n|92,808 (100,0%)\n|86,826 (100,0%)\n|-\n|Serbs\n|91,784 (85,21%)\n|57,389 (59,17%)\n|56,029 (60,37%)\n|60,595 (69,79%)\n|-\n|Bosniaks\n|13,090 (12,15%)\n|30,229 (31,17%)\n|24,282 (26,16%)\n|23,343 (26,88%)\n|-\n|Others\n|793 (0,736%)\n|4,452 (4,590%)\n|1,155 (1,245%)\n|649 (0,747%)\n|-\n|Una